flowchart LR
    admin[System Admin]
    upstream[HTTPS Threat Feed]

    subgraph controlPlane [Control Plane]
        api[Feeds API]
        postgres[(PostgreSQL<br/>sources · runs · assertions<br/>global deny state)]
        redis[(Redis Job Queue)]
    end

    subgraph worker [Agent Worker]
        scheduler[Due-time Scheduler]
        processor[Job Processor]
        fetcher[Bounded Background<br/>Feed Fetcher]
        reconciler[Assertion Reconciler]
        applier[Global Deny Applier]
    end

    subgraph dataPlane [Data Plane]
        helper[xdpgw-apply<br/>global mode]
        maps[(Inactive Slot Maps<br/>global bloom · LPM · meta)]
        xdp[XDP Hot Path]
    end

    admin -->|Manages and requests sync| api
    api -->|Persists and audits| postgres
    api -->|Post-commit job ID| redis
    scheduler -->|Queries due sources| postgres
    scheduler -->|Enqueues FEED_SYNC| redis
    redis -->|Delivers job ID| processor
    processor --> fetcher
    fetcher -->|HTTPS GET, no redirects| upstream
    fetcher -->|Validated CIDRs| reconciler
    reconciler -->|Assertions, overlaps, desired digest| postgres
    reconciler -->|Changed desired set| applier
    applier -->|Versioned global snapshot| helper
    helper -->|Carry services, rebuild global, verify| maps
    helper -->|Atomic active_config flip| xdp
